     I stand now, 55 seasons later, many friend and foe lay motionless in my wake of fury.  Glimpses of mana drip from my experienced hands, countless journeys are worn on my feet, and my eyes sparkle like lightning and tell the story of a thousand tales.  I look back up at Jabanik still hovering upon my side, my best friend.  My tiny back is pressed against the rough walls of the mighty castle, elbows propped up with my small knees.  'We have been through a lot,' I tell my only companion with a heavy heart, and I shed a tear.  He looks back down upon me with a warm smile, but cold eyes, and does not say a word.  I rise to my feet, and see the veins in Jabanik's hands expand as he grasps the cold steel of his swords tightly.  It is time to continue to where I see no end, and we disappear into the depths of the castle together...  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub28.ezboard.com/ucolossis.showPublicProfile?language=EN>colossis</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>SPACE MONKEY!!!</span><br>  Posts: 40<br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/11/02 11:10:17 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub28.ezboard.com/fdrinal28133frm11.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=41.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Karnors Castle</span><hr size=1> nice ! <p><center><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=62680">Sibian's  Pimp Gettho Loot.</a><center>
